### GET item
GET http://localhost:3000/items HTTP/1.1

### GET item by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/items/2 HTTP/1.1

### GET all pokemon
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon/4 HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon by name
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon/pikachu HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with filters (attack range)
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon?attack_min=100&attack_max=150 HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with filters and sorting
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon?attack_min=100&sort=attack&order=desc HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon?hp_min=50&attack_min=80&price_max=5000&bst_min=400 HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with pagination (first page, default limit 20)
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with custom limit
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon?limit=10 HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with offset and limit (second page)
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon?offset=20&limit=20 HTTP/1.1

### GET pokemon with filters, sorting, and pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon?attack_min=100&sort=attack&order=desc&offset=0&limit=10 HTTP/1.1

### GET budget picks (best BST for price)
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon/budget-picks HTTP/1.1

### GET budget picks with budget filter
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon/budget-picks?budget=400 HTTP/1.1

### GET health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health HTTP/1.1